Params[3]: All this is too much for a human child to handle. Let's find a place to rest.
Seeing the sad look on the girl's face, HNB1 pats her consolingly on the head.
A few hours of rest won't hurt. Are you hungry? I heard your stomach growl.
Am not! My tummy didn't growl!
It's okay. I won't laugh at you.
I'll go look for something to eat. Find somewhere nearby for her to rest, G3.
